value.0: Cradossk is a legendary Trandoshan bounty hunter who leads the Bounty Hunters Guild. He is also the father of the notorious bounty hunter Bossk. He built up a fearsome reputation during his time as a hunter, and it was said that even Boba Fett held some respect for him. However, with age, even he started to decline in strength. His son, Bossk, grew resentful of the elderly lizard as he saw more and more weakness within him.

The EE-3 carbine rifle is a blaster that was modeled after the E-11 blaster rifle used by Imperial Stormtroopers. The rifle consisted of a small handle attached to a long circular barrel. An alternate version of this model features a modified scope mounting and hand grips that run the length of the barrel.

The EE-3 was used famously by the bounty hunter Boba Fett. Fett modified his by adding a stock and an electronic scope for sniping, making it a dangerous weapon. Prince Xizor also used an EE-3 to try to kill Luke Skywalker as the Jedi and his friends escaped the Falleen's palace on Coruscant.

A blaster is a ranged weapon that fires bursts of particle beam energy called blaster bolts from a replaceable power cell. The most commonly used weapon in the Galaxy, blasters' intense beams consisting of compacted high-energy particles and intense light can kill or paralyze their target, depending on their setting.

Bossk (meaning "Devours His Prey" in Dosh) is a Trandoshan bounty hunter and the pilot of the Hound's Tooth. He also holds the title of Monarch of the Qotile system. He is particularly unfond of Chewbacca and his Human partner Han Solo. He has faced them several times.

He is also a frequent partner and foe of both Boba Fett and Zuckuss, both fellow bounty hunters. After being repeatedly beaten by Boba Fett, he boosted his reputation as a bounty hunter by "defeating" him on Tatooine.

Zuckuss is a successful Gand bounty hunter, referred to as "The Uncanny One" by his fellow hunters, Zuckuss is renowned for his ability to discover hidden quarry. His tracking skills derive both from his training as a findsman and from his innate Force-sensitivity, allowing him to sense individuals at range and sense the motives of his prey.

During his long career, Zuckuss has had many associates but was known primarily to partner with the droid 4-LOM - the two make a formidable bounty hunting team. Due to his famed abilities, Zuckuss is highly sought after, and he has found employment with the Bounty Hunters Guild, the Hutt Cartel, TaggeCo, and even the Rebellion at times.

Although incredibly successful, Zuckuss is not without major flaws. He is plagued with schizophrenia and an advanced case of multiple personality disorder which causes him to speak in two different dialects. Despite his mental health, Zuckuss became incredibly popular on his homeworld of Gand, eventually inspiring an entire generation of Gand bounty hunters to seek success off-world.
